trans-unit.source: The type of the keys in the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 字典中的索引鍵類型。

trans-unit.source: The type of the values in the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 字典中的值類型。

trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of key/value pairs that are sorted on the key.
trans-unit.target: 代表根據索引鍵，所排序的索引鍵/值組集合。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> generic class is a binary search tree with O(log `n`) retrieval, where `n` is the number of elements in the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>泛型類別是與 O 二進位搜尋樹狀目錄 (記錄`n`) 擷取其中`n`是字典中的項目數。

trans-unit.source: In this respect, it is similar to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602> generic class.
trans-unit.target: 在這一方面，它是類似於<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602>泛型類別。

trans-unit.source: The two classes have similar object models, and both have O(log `n`) retrieval.
trans-unit.target: 兩個類別都具有類似的物件模型，且兩者都有 O (記錄`n`) 擷取。

trans-unit.source: Where the two classes differ is in memory use and speed of insertion and removal:
trans-unit.target: 兩個類別的不同之處是記憶體使用量和速度的插入和移除：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602> uses less memory than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602> 使用較少的記憶體比<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> has faster insertion and removal operations for unsorted data: O(log `n`) as opposed to O(`n`) for <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> 具有未排序的資料的快速插入和移除作業： O (記錄`n`) 而不是 O (`n`) 的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602>。

trans-unit.source: If the list is populated all at once from sorted data, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602> is faster than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>.
trans-unit.target: 如果從已排序的資料，會同時填入此清單<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedList%602>的速度比<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>。

trans-unit.source: Each key/value pair can be retrieved as a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602> structure, or as a <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> through the nongeneric <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> interface.
trans-unit.target: 每個索引鍵/值組可以擷取為<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>結構，或為<xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>透過非泛型<xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>介面。

trans-unit.source: Keys must be immutable as long as they are used as keys in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>.
trans-unit.target: 只要使用中索引鍵，索引鍵必須是不可變<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>。

trans-unit.source: Every key in a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> must be unique.
trans-unit.target: 在每個索引鍵<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>必須是唯一的。

trans-unit.source: A key cannot be `null`, but a value can be, if the value type `TValue` is a reference type.
trans-unit.target: 金鑰不能`null`，但是值可以是，如果型別值`TValue`是參考型別。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> requires a comparer implementation to perform key comparisons.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> 需要執行比較索引鍵比較子實作。

trans-unit.source: You can specify an implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> generic interface by using a constructor that accepts a `comparer` parameter; if you do not specify an implementation, the default genericcomparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> is used.
trans-unit.target: 您可以指定的實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601>使用建構函式可接受泛型介面`comparer`參數; 如果您未指定，預設 genericcomparer 實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>用。

trans-unit.source: If type `TKey` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601?displayProperty=nameWithType> generic interface, the default comparer uses that implementation.
trans-unit.target: 如果型別`TKey`實作<xref:System.IComparable%601?displayProperty=nameWithType>泛型介面，則預設比較子會使用該實作。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) returns an object of the type of the elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 傳回集合中的項目類型的物件。

trans-unit.source: Since each element of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602> is a key/value pair, the element type is not the type of the key or the type of the value.
trans-unit.target: 因為每個項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602>是索引鍵/值組，項目型別不是索引鍵的類型或值的類型。

trans-unit.source: Instead, the element type is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>.
trans-unit.target: 相反地，項目型別是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>。

trans-unit.source: Any instance members are not guaranteed to be thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 不保證任何執行個體成員是安全執行緒。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary`2" /> can support multiple readers concurrently, as long as the collection is not modified.

trans-unit.source: Even so, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 即便如此，列舉集合在本質上並非安全執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of enumerators.

trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: The dictionary is maintained in a sorted order using an internal tree.
trans-unit.target: 使用內部的樹狀結構以排序順序維護的字典。

trans-unit.source: Every new element is positioned at the correct sort position, and the tree is adjusted to maintain the sort order whenever an element is removed.
trans-unit.target: 每個新的項目位於正確的排序位置與維護的排序次序，每當移除項目會調整樹狀目錄。

trans-unit.source: While enumerating, the sort order is maintained.
trans-unit.target: 列舉，會維護排序順序。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 此位置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A>未定義屬性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您必須呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法，以將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same element until the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A>屬性會傳回相同的項目，直到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法呼叫。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.SortedDictionary%602.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> method also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>方法也會列舉值帶回至這個位置。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 此位置<xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A>未定義屬性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您必須呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法，以將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> property returns the same object until either <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A>屬性會傳回相同的物件直到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>呼叫。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: To set <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> to the first element of the collection again, you can call <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> followed by <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 若要再次將 <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Entry%2A> 設定為集合的第一個元素，您可以在呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 之後，接著呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空間中集合的預設實作未同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" />，可用於逐一查看集合。

trans-unit.source: For purposes of enumeration, each item is a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602> structure representing a value and its key.
trans-unit.target: 列舉的目的而言，每個項目是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>結構，表示值和其索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` Visual Basic) hides the complexity of enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + + `For Each` Visual Basic) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 此位置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>未定義屬性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您必須呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法，以將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> property returns the same element until the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>屬性會傳回相同的項目，直到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法呼叫。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空間中集合的預設實作未同步處理。
